sub_title: Key Account Manager MEA at Chromaflo Technologies Europe BV
summary:
Sales professional with a deep understanding of consumer behaviour, strong communicative and management skills and international experience in both sales and account management. A varied skill set that combines comprehensive knowledge of the business, a good understanding of key customer goals, a collaborative and strategic mindset with effective communication in multiple languages. 

Specialties: Multilingual (English, French, German, Dutch, Turkish and Spanish)

Sales Management, Key Account Management, International Sales B2B, Business Strategy, Product Development, Product Management, Business Development, Project Management.
